00:02:17.830 --> 00:02:23.820
Before I start
diving into my story,

00:02:23.820 --> 00:02:26.660
I want you to know that I'm
predominantly right brained.

00:02:26.660 --> 00:02:29.390
I wrote this book
cinemagraphically

00:02:29.390 --> 00:02:32.400
because I'm first and
foremost an artist.

00:02:32.400 --> 00:02:35.850
And the practices of filming
help me bridge my experience

00:02:35.850 --> 00:02:39.190
