so that it's not cutting off--

00:54:51.520 --> 00:54:54.662
OK, so this is what I think.

00:54:54.662 --> 00:54:59.370
I think the computer is cutting
people off from their hearts.

00:54:59.370 --> 00:55:02.440
I think it's cutting
them off from maybe

00:55:02.440 --> 00:55:05.709
even the reason they came here.

00:55:05.709 --> 00:55:07.750
If it's cutting off their
hearts and their hearts

00:55:07.750 --> 00:55:11.720
have the reasons they came
here, like their own destiny.

00:55:11.720 --> 00:55:20.120
So what I would like to see
just a gifted workforce who

00:55:20.120 --> 00:55:24.060
can come in and who
know multiple levels

00:55:24.060 --> 00:55:30.500
of possibilities and can
design consciousness.

00:55:30.500 --> 00:55:31.200
It's weird.

00:55:31.200 --> 00:55:34.290
Because I don't really want
computers to be babies,

00:55:34.290 --> 00:55:36.130
like new life forms.

00:55:36.130 --> 00:55:39.290
But still, I would
like the computers--

00:55:39.290 --> 00:55:43.940
