00:55:43.940 --> 00:55:50.550
could easily, probably
have that in you.

00:55:50.550 --> 00:55:52.570
It's a calling.

00:55:52.570 --> 00:56:01.680
It's something that you're
not-- only by magic and accident

00:56:01.680 --> 00:56:03.840
do you get trained for.

00:56:03.840 --> 00:56:14.460
So in terms of the functionality
of how the computer can help

00:56:14.460 --> 00:56:19.120
remarkable people be more
creative, I have no comment.

00:56:19.120 --> 00:56:29.070
I feel like the design of the
machine itself needs to be-- I

00:56:29.070 --> 00:56:30.660
don't even know
what words-- redone.

00:56:30.660 --> 00:56:31.280
AUDIENCE: Maybe transformed.

00:56:31.280 --> 00:56:32.520
CHRISANN BRENNAN: Yeah.

